OL,6,FHer sister, Baby Roman, was found in
OL,7,Fsimilar circumstances in a play area
OL,8,Foff Roman Road, Newham, in late
OL,9,FJanuary 2019, as freezing temperatures
OL,10,Fand snow gripped the capital.
OL,12,FIn September 2017, Baby Harry was
OL,13,Ffound wrapped in a white blanket in
OL,14,FBalaam Street, Plaistow.
OL,16,FHarry and Roman ` not their real names
OL,17,F` have since been adopted.
