OL,9,Fthat the ongoing investigation means
OL,10,Fthat Elsa's birth cannot be
OL,11,Fregistered, meaning no final decision
OL,12,Fregarding her care can be made.
OL,14,FA further hearing in her case is
OL,15,Fexpected to be held at a later date.
