OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Laurence Dight,
OL,7,Ffrom the Metropolitan Police, told the
OL,8,Fcourt on Monday that the police
OL,9,Finvestigation into the identity of the
OL,10,Fparents remained ongoing, with anyone
OL,11,Fwith information as to the parents'
OL,12,Fidentities asked to contact the force
OL,13,Fusing the reference CAD 6876/18 Jan.
OL,15,FA change in reporting restrictions
OL,17,FOn Monday, Judge Carol Atkinson ruled
OL,18,Frestrictions should be lifted to allow
OL,19,Fthe reporting of the relationship
OL,20,Fbetween the children, claiming it was
OL,21,Fneeded for the "openness of justice".
