OL,7,Finterest in reporting this story.
OL,9,F"The abandonment of a baby in this
OL,10,Fcountry is a very, very unusual event
OL,11,Fand there are years where there are no
OL,12,Fchildren abandoned, and because of
OL,13,Fthat it is the story of the abandoning
OL,14,Fof a child that is of public interest."
