OL,6,FShe continued: "It is for the same
OL,7,Freason, in our current society, of
OL,8,Fenormous interest and importance that
OL,9,Fpeople know that there is a mother and
OL,10,Ffather out there who felt the need to
OL,11,Frelinquish their children in this way,
OL,12,Fthree times, and that is of
OL,13,Fconsiderable interest, it seems to me.
OL,15,F"If I restrict these rights and the
OL,16,Freporting of that story, I think that
OL,17,Fdoes impact on public consciousness of
OL,18,Fthese sorts of matters. It restricts
OL,19,Fthe openness of justice."
