OL,6,FWhile journalists can usually attend
OL,7,Ffamily court proceedings, reporting
OL,8,Frestrictions limit what can be
OL,9,Fpublished to protect the anonymity of
OL,10,Fthose involved.
OL,12,FA pilot scheme to increase
OL,13,Ftransparency in the family court
OL,14,Fsystem, which began with three courts
OL,15,Fin 2023, was expanded earlier this
OL,16,Fyear to allow accredited journalists
OL,17,Fand legal bloggers to report on cases
OL,18,Fat 16 courts across England and Wales.
