OL,6,FJudges can set out what details may be
OL,7,Freported under a Transparency Order,
OL,8,Fwith journalists also allowed to
OL,9,Faccess some documents.
OL,11,FFollowing an application made by PA
OL,12,Fand the BBC, Judge Atkinson varied the
OL,13,FTransparency Order in Elsa's case to
OL,14,Fallow reporting of the fact she has
OL,15,Ftwo siblings and other details.
OL,17,FOnly certain other details of the
OL,18,Fthree children may be reported.
OL,20,F"All three children are safe"
